*Verify:* Returns self\n37:   - *Test:* `with AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient(...) as client:`\n38: \n39: - [ ] **T006** Add `__exit__` to AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n40:   - *File:* `agentcube/clients/agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n41:   - *Verify:* Calls `close()`, re-raises exception\n42:   - *Test:* Exception in with block triggers cleanup\n43: \n44: ---\n45: \n46: ### Phase 2: Unit Tests - HTTP Session (T007-T011)\n47: \n48: - [ ] **T007** Test create_session returns Session with HTTPAdapter\n49:   - *File:* `tests/test_http_session.py`\n50:   - *Verify:* Session has adapter mounted for http:// and https://\n51:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_http_session.py::test_create_session_with_adapter`\n52: \n53: - [ ] **T008** Test create_session with custom pool settings\n54:   - *File:* `tests/test_http_session.py`\n55:   - *Verify:* pool_connections=5, pool_maxsize=20\n56:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_http_session.py::test_create_session_custom_pools`\n57: \n58: - [ ] **T009** Test ControlPlaneClient context manager cleanup on normal exit\n59:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n60:   - *Verify:* Session closed after with block\n61:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_context_manager_normal_exit`\n62: \n63: - [ ] **T010** Test ControlPlaneClient context manager cleanup on exception\n64:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n65:   - *Verify:* Session closed, exception re-raised\n66:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_context_manager_exception`\n67: \n68: - [ ] **T011** Test CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient context manager\n69:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n70:   - *Verify:* Session closed on exit\n71:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_context_manager`\n72: \n73: ---\n74: \n75: ### Phase 3: Unit Tests - Headers & Timeouts (T012-T017)\n76: \n77: - [ ] **T012** Test Authorization header set when token provided\n78:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n79:   - *Verify:* Header contains \"Bearer {token}\"\n80:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_auth_header_set`\n81: \n82: - [ ] **T013** Test No Authorization header when token is empty\n83:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n84:   - *Verify:* Authorization header not in request\n85:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_no_auth_header`\n86: \n87: - [ ] **T014** Test x-agentcube-session-id header in CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient\n88:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n89:   - *Verify:* Header present in requests\n90:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_session_header`\n91: \n92: - [ ] **T015** Test x-agentcube-session-id header in AgentRuntimeDataPlaneClient\n93:   - *File:* `tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py`\n94:   - *Verify:* Header present in requests\n95:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_agent_runtime_data_plane.py::test_session_header`\n96: \n97: - [ ] **T016** Test timeout tuple construction\n98:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n99:   - *Verify:* timeout=(connect_timeout, self.timeout)\n100:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_timeout_tuple`\n101: \n102: - [ ] **T017** Test per-call timeout override (timeout + 2.0)\n103:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n104:   - *Verify:* execute_command(timeout=60) uses 62s read timeout\n105:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_per_call_timeout`\n106: \n107: ---\n108: \n109: ### Phase 4: Unit Tests - URL & Body (T018-T022)\n110: \n111: - [ ] **T018** Test ControlPlaneClient base_url from env var\n112:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n113:   - *Verify:* WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL env var used\n114:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_base_url_from_env`\n115: \n116: - [ ] **T019** Test ControlPlaneClient base_url from argument\n117:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane.py`\n118:   - *Verify:* Argument takes precedence over env var\n119:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane.py::test_base_url_from_arg`\n120: \n121: - [ ] **T020** Test CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient URL construction\n122:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n123:   - *Verify:* URL format: `/v1/namespaces/{ns}/code-interpreters/{cr}/invocations/`\n124:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_url_construction`\n125: \n126: - [ ] **T021** Test execute_command request body format\n127:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n128:   - *Verify:* `{\"command\": [...], \"timeout\": \"60s\"}`\n129:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_execute_command_body`\n130: \n131: - [ ] **T022** Test write_file base64 encoding\n132:   - *File:* `tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py`\n133:   - *Verify:* Content is base64 encoded in body\n134:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_code_interpreter_data_plane.py::test_write_file_encoding`\n135: \n136: ---\n137: \n138: ### Phase 5: Unit Tests - Token & Logging (T023-T027)\n139: \n140: - [ ] **T023** Test read_token_from_file with existing file\n141:   - *File:* `tests/test_utils.py`\n142:   - *Verify:* Returns token string (stripped)\n143:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_utils.py::test_read_token_from_file_exists`\n144: \n145: - [ ] **T024** Test read_token_from_file with missing file\n146:   - *File:* `tests/test_utils.py`\n147:   - *Verify:* Returns None, no exception\n148:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_utils.py::test_read_token_from_file_missing`\n149: \n150: - [ ] **T025** Test get_logger default level (INFO)\n151:   - *File:* `tests/test_log.py`\n152:   - *Verify:* Logger level is INFO\n153:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_log.py::test_logger_default_level`\n154: \n155: - [ ] **T026** Test get_logger with verbose=True (DEBUG)\n156:   - *File:* `tests/test_log.py`\n157:   - *Verify:* Logger level is DEBUG\n158:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_log.py::test_logger_verbose`\n159: \n160: - [ ] **T027** Test exception hierarchy\n161:   - *File:* `tests/test_exceptions.py`\n162:   - *Verify:* All exceptions inherit from AgentCubeError\n163:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_exceptions.py::test_exception_hierarchy`\n164: \n165: ---\n166: \n167: ### Phase 6: Integration & Lint (T028-T030)\n168: \n169: - [ ] **T028** Run all AR-029 unit tests\n170:   - *Verify:* All pytest tests pass\n171:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/ -v --tb=short 2>&1 | grep -E \"(PASSED|FAILED|ERROR)\"`\n172: \n173: - [ ] **T029** Test ControlPlaneClient with mock server\n174:   - *File:* `tests/test_control_plane_integration.py`\n175:   - *Verify:* create_session and delete_session work with mock HTTP\n176:   - *Test:* `pytest tests/test_control_plane_integration.py`\n177: \n178: - [ ] **T030** Run linter/typecheck on all modified files\n179:   - *Verify:* ruff and mypy pass\n180:   - *Test:* `ruff check agentcube/ && mypy agentcube/`\n181: \n182: ---\n183: \n184: ## Dependencies\n185: \n186: | Task | Depends On |\n187: |------|------------|\n188: | T002 | T001 |\n189: | T004 | T003 |\n190: | T006 | T005 |\n191: | T008 | T007 |\n192: | T009 | T001, T002 |\n193: | T010 | T001, T002 |\n194: | T011 | T003, T004 |\n195: | T012 | T001, T002 |\n196: | T013 | T001, T002 |\n197: | T014 | T003, T004 |\n198: | T015 | T005, T006 |\n199: | T016 | T003 |\n200: | T017 | T003 |\n201: | T018 | T001 |\n202: | T019 | T001 |\n203: | T020 | T003 |\n204: | T021 | T003 |\n205: | T022 | T003 |\n206: | T023 | - |\n207: | T024 | - |\n208: | T025 | - |\n209: | T026 | - |\n210: | T027 | - |\n211: | T028 | T007-T027 |\n212: | T029 | T001-T006 |\n213: | T030 | T001-T029 |\n214: \n215: ---\n216: \n217: ## Verification Checklist\n218: \n219: - [ ] AC001: create_session returns Session with HTTPAdapter for http/https\n220: - [ ] AC002: Context manager closes session on exit\n221: - [ ] AC003: Connect timeout raises ConnectTimeout\n222: - [ ] AC004: Read timeout raises ReadTimeout\n223: - [ ] AC005: Authorizati