{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775872738293,"sessionID":"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy","part":{"id":"prt_d7a42fb61001KNEQ657xoLjth1","messageID":"msg_d7a42df94001WkdBavu3ku0xvk","sessionID":"ses_285bda408ffee9I6x6R12bAjXy","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_fcbcd5f8f9154091805c3d90","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-031 — RBAC Configuration (SA/Role/Binding) Tasks\n\n**Module:** manifests  \n**Language:** YAML (Helm)  \n**Size:** M  \n**Stage:** ST-3 (Design Completed)\n\n---\n\n## Implementation Tasks\n\n### Phase 1: ServiceAccount Multi-Component Support (T001-T003)\n\n- [ ] **T001** Extend ServiceAccount template to support multiple SAs\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/serviceaccount.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* Template renders 3 ServiceAccounts: router-sa, agentd-controller-sa, workload-manager-sa\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep -c \"kind: ServiceAccount\" # should be 3`\n\n- [ ] **T002** Add router ServiceAccount to values.yaml\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.serviceAccounts.router.name` exists with default value \"agentcube-router-sa\"\n  - *Test:* Check rendered template contains \"agentcube-router-sa\"\n\n- [ ] **T003** Add workload-manager ServiceAccount to values.yaml\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.serviceAccounts.workloadManager.name` exists with default value \"agentcube-workload-manager-sa\"\n  - *Test:* Check rendered template contains \"agentcube-workload-manager-sa\"\n\n---\n\n### Phase 2: ClusterRole Separation (T004-T006)\n\n- [ ] **T004** Create separate agentd-controller ClusterRole\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrole-agentd.yaml` (new file)\n  - *Verify:* Rules include pods, services, secrets, configmaps, events, CRDs, sandboxes\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep \"kind: ClusterRole\" | wc -l # should be 2+`\n\n- [ ] **T005** Create router ClusterRole (read-only)\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrole-router.yaml` (new file)\n  - *Verify:* Rules include only get, list, watch on agentruntimes and secrets\n  - *Test:* Check rendered ClusterRole has no create/update/patch/delete verbs\n\n- [ ] **T006** Update agentd-controller ClusterRole rules per design\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrole.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* Rules include pod/exec verb for sandbox access\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep -A5 \"kind: ClusterRole\" | grep \"exec\"`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 3: ClusterRoleBinding Multi-Binding (T007-T009)\n\n- [ ] **T007** Create router ClusterRoleBinding\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrolebinding-router.yaml` (new file)\n  - *Verify:* Binds router-sa to router ClusterRole\n  - *Test:* Check rendered binding references router ClusterRole and router-sa\n\n- [ ] **T008** Create agentd ClusterRoleBinding\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrolebinding-agentd.yaml` (new file)\n  - *Verify:* Binds agentd-controller-sa to agentd ClusterRole\n  - *Test:* Check rendered binding references agentd ClusterRole\n\n- [ ] **T009** Update main ClusterRoleBinding to use correct SA\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrolebinding.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* References agentcube-controller-sa (not generic)\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep -A10 \"kind: ClusterRoleBinding\" | grep \"name: agentcube\"`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 4: Namespace-scoped Role/RoleBinding (T010-T011)\n\n- [ ] **T010** Create Role template for workload-manager\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/role.yaml` (new file)\n  - *Verify:* Namespace-scoped Role with sandboxes and CRD permissions\n  - *Test:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube | grep \"kind: Role\"`\n\n- [ ] **T011** Create RoleBinding template for workload-manager\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/rolebinding.yaml` (new file)\n  - *Verify:* Binds workload-manager-sa to workload-manager Role\n  - *Test:* Check rendered RoleBinding references correct Role and SA\n\n---\n\n### Phase 5: Helm Helpers (T012-T013)\n\n- [ ] **T012** Add helper functions for SA names\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n  - *Verify:* Functions: `agentcube.routerSAName`, `agentcube.agentdControllerSAName`, `agentcube.workloadManagerSAName`\n  - *Test:* `grep -E \"define.*SA\" manifests/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n\n- [ ] **T013** Add helper functions for Role/ClusterRole names\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n  - *Verify:* Functions: `agentcube.routerRoleName`, `agentcube.agentdRoleName`, `agentcube.workloadManagerRoleName`\n  - *Test:* `grep -E \"define.*Role\" manifests/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 6: Values & Conditional Rendering (T014-T016)\n\n- [ ] **T014** Add per-SA enable flags to values.yaml\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.serviceAccounts.router.create`, `rbac.serviceAccounts.agentd.create`, `rbac.serviceAccounts.workloadManager.create`\n  - *Test:* `helm template --set rbac.serviceAccounts.router.create=false | grep -c \"agentcube-router-sa\"`\n\n- [ ] **T015** Add per-Role enable flags to values.yaml\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.clusterRoles.router.create`, `rbac.clusterRoles.agentd.create`\n  - *Test:* Check template conditionals use these flags\n\n- [ ] **T016** Add namespace-scoped Role enable flag\n  - *File:* `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.role.create` and `rbac.roleBinding.create` flags exist\n  - *Test:* `helm template --set rbac.role.create=false | grep -c \"kind: Role\" # should be 0`\n\n---\n\n### Phase 7: Validation & Testing (T017-T019)\n\n- [ ] **T017** Validate Helm template rendering\n  - *Verify:* `helm template agentcube ./manifests/agentcube --debug > /dev/null` succeeds\n  - *Test:* `helm lint ./manifests/agentcube`\n\n- [ ] **T018** Verify all RBAC resources render correctly\n  - *Verify:* 3 ServiceAccounts, 3 ClusterRoles, 2+ ClusterRoleBindings, 1 Role, 1 RoleBinding\n  - *Test:* Count rendered resources\n\n- [ ] **T019** Test RBAC disable toggle\n  - *Verify:* `rbac.create: false` renders no RBAC resources\n  - *Test:* `helm template --set rbac.create=false ./manifests/agentcube | grep -c \"kind: ServiceAccount\" # should be 0`\n\n---\n\n## Dependencies\n\n| Task | Depends On |\n|------|------------|\n| T002 | T001 |\n| T003 | T001 |\n| T004 | T001 |\n| T005 | T004 |\n| T006 | T004 |\n| T007 | T001, T005 |\n| T008 | T001, T004 |\n| T009 | T001, T006 |\n| T010 | T001, T003 |\n| T011 | T010 |\n| T012 | - |\n| T013 | T012 |\n| T014 | T001, T002, T003 |\n| T015 | T004, T005, T006 |\n| T016 | T010, T011 |\n| T017 | T001-T016 |\n| T018 | T001-T016 |\n| T019 | T014, T015, T016 |\n\n---\n\n## Verification Checklist\n\n- [ ] AC001: 3 ServiceAccounts render (router-sa, agentd-controller-sa, workload-manager-sa)\n- [ ] AC002: Router ClusterRole has only read-only permissions\n- [ ] AC003: Agentd ClusterRole has full CRUD + pod/exec permissions\n- [ ] AC004: Workload-manager Role has namespace-scoped permissions\n- [ ] AC005: All ClusterRoleBindings reference correct ClusterRoles\n- [ ] AC006: RoleBinding binds workload-manager-sa to correct Role\n- [ ] AC007: Helper functions generate correct names\n- [ ] AC008: Per-component enable flags work correctly\n- [ ] AC009: `rbac.create: false` disables all RBAC resources\n- [ ] AC010: Helm lint passes\n- [ ] AC011: Template renders without errors\n- [ ] AC012: Values.yaml has all RBAC configuration keys\n\n---\n\n## References\n\n- Design: `manifests/agentcube/design.md`\n- ServiceAccount template: `manifests/agentcube/templates/serviceaccount.yaml`\n- ClusterRole template: `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrole.yaml`\n- ClusterRoleBinding template: `manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrolebinding.yaml`\n- Values: `manifests/agentcube/values.yaml`\n- Helpers: `manifests/agentcube/templates/_helpers.tpl`\n\n---\n\n## Notes\n\n- Current implementation has 1 SA, 1 ClusterRole, 1 ClusterRoleBinding\n- Design specifies 3 SAs, 3 ClusterRoles, 3+ bindings, plus namespace-scoped Role/RoleBinding\n- Stage ST-3 marked complete in design.md - tasks cover remaining implementation","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/changes/AR-031/tasks.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-MiniMax-M2.5_20260410T163134Z/manifests/agentcube/templates/clusterrole.yaml\">\nERROR [1:3] Block collections are not allowed within flow collections\nERROR [1:5] Missing , or : between flow map items\nERROR [4:1] Unexpected flow-map-start at node end\nERROR [4:2] Unexpected flow-map-start at node end\nERROR [4:3] Unexpected seq-item-ind at node end\nERROR [4:5] Unexpected scalar at node end\nERROR [4:28] Unexpected flow-map-end token in YAML stream: \"}\"\nERROR [4:29] Unexpected flow-map-end token in YAML stream: \"}\"\nERROR [5:1] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"apiVersion\"\nERROR [5:11] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [5:13] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"rbac.authorization.k8s.io/v1\"\nERROR [6:1] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"kind\"\nERROR [6:5] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [6:7] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"ClusterRole\"\nERROR [7:1] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"metadata\"\nERROR [7:9] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [8:3] Unexpected scalar token in YAML stream: \"name\"\nERROR [8:7] Unexpected map-value-ind token in YAML stream: \":\"\nERROR [8:9] Unexpected flow-map-start token in YAML stream: \"{\"\nERROR [8:10] Unexpected flow-map-start token in YAML stream: \"{\"\n... and 45 more\n</di